<h4 id="werking-transistor">Werking transistor</h4>

<p><img src="https://i.imgur.com/6zkF2eV.png =x250" alt="" /></p>

<p>$I_c=I_b\times H_{fe}$
$I_e=I_c+I_b$</p>

<p><a href="http://tinyurl.com/yx39cser">Simulatie</a></p>

<hr />

<p><img src="https://i.imgur.com/i1i228B.png" alt="" /></p>

