<hr />

<h4 id="summary">Summary</h4>
<ul>
  <li>$H_{FE}$ DC current gain</li>
  <li>$V_{BE}$ Base emitter forward voltage</li>
  <li>$I_C$ Collector Current</li>
</ul>

