<p><img src="https://i.imgur.com/9D3g5lj.png =x450" alt="" /></p>

<hr />

<p><img src="https://i.imgur.com/RqkpvRf.png" alt="" /></p>

<hr />

<p><a href="http://tinyurl.com/y8f9humm">Simulatie</a></p>

<hr />

<p><a href="https://www.sparkfun.com/products/10213">Example mosfet</a></p>

<hr />

<h4 id="summary-1">Summary</h4>
<ul>
  <li>$V_{DS}$ Drain-Source Breakdown Voltage</li>
  <li>$V_{GS(th)}$ Gate Threshold Voltage</li>
  <li>$V_{GS(on)}$ Static Drain-Source On-Resistance</li>
  <li>$I_D$ Drain Current</li>
</ul>

