<p><img src="https://i.imgur.com/hl52ctI.png" alt="" /></p>

<p><a href="http://tinyurl.com/rftlt8t">Simulatie</a></p>

<p>note: waarom voorschakelweerstand?</p>

<hr />

<h4 id="voorschakelweerstand-berekening">Voorschakelweerstand: berekening</h4>
<p>$U_R = \dfrac{Bronspanning - U_{LED}}{Stroom\ door\ LED}$</p>

<p><img src="https://i.imgur.com/hl52ctI.png" alt="" /></p>

<p>note:
Power supply: 5V 
Led voltage = 1.78V
Led Current = 10mA</p>

<p>Ur = 5V - 1.8V = 3.2V 
R = U / I = 3.2V / 0.01A = 320$\Omega$</p>

<hr />

